@startuml
actor User
participant MainLayoutComponent
participant BreakpointService
participant Router

User -> MainLayoutComponent : open app
MainLayoutComponent -> BreakpointService : read viewport
BreakpointService --> MainLayoutComponent : mobile / tablet / desktop
MainLayoutComponent -> Router : render route shell
User -> MainLayoutComponent : resize / navigate
MainLayoutComponent -> BreakpointService : recalculate
MainLayoutComponent --> User : adaptive nav UI
@enduml
